data.description: Looking for a getaway or potential new vacation rental? This charming, well cared for home offers opportunity for your personal use, or could be included in your investment strategy. Enjoy the nearby recreational activities and the views of Cooney Reservoir and the Beartooth Mountains. The beloved town of Red Lodge and conveniences of Billings are less than an hour away. Located on the property is a 30'x35' shop with electricity and a 50amp RV hook-up. Inside, there's no shortage of storage with 2 closets in the bedroom and a loft above. The bathroom offers a tiled shower to give the home a luxurious feel. The kitchen boasts a generous amount of cabinet and counter space. To top it off, the covered front porch is the perfect spot to enjoy the sunshine. This is a de-titled, manufactured home on a magnum foundation. 2200gal cistern. Come see it today!
